caption: Nice place to take your kid along and learn about different fields of science.

A structure rich in stairs, even labyrinthine, a large space on the upper floor. Perfect for buffets and other scientific experiments of all kinds. Special mention to the toilets, whose walls are decorated with drawings which are -really- worth the detour. Bravo to the artists of these unknown masterpieces.

Inside the ESPCI ParisTech, a fun space for the whole family with activities for all levels and ages of our little ones. Interactions between the presenters, ESPCI ParisTech students and the young and old public. The young scientists, future engineers of the school, in a popularization approach, know how to interest young and old alike. Without realizing it, we even learn complex physical concepts without it causing a headache. Interesting even for the very big children that we all parents are.
Coming for a very nice exhibition on influences and choices, I was able to discover a very informative workshop for little tinkerers, led by a scientist who is very comfortable with children
great initiation the discovery of physics should be offered from primary school I remember a similar program produced by Disney and broadcast on Thursday afternoons on the ortf... is it dated?

A very pleasant place, pleasant for adults and children alike. For children from 7/8 years old, interesting and free activities on Wednesday and Saturday afternoons
Great place to discover the science of yesterday and tomorrow, in the heart of ESPCI. There are friendly scientific mediators and lots of passionate researchers!
Very interesting, friendly place, very good for introducing children to science
An exciting experience of reflection and play around science, to do with or without children!
